			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Use Debug Book to travel to Act 1b -> Creche - Main Creche floor\r\nGet through the dialog with the guards at the checkpoint (you'll likely need to use killcombat in recon)\r\nOnce through the doors go left (west), then right (north), and enter the Hatchery Chamber through the door at the end of the corridor.\r\nSpeak to the guard to the right (north) as you enter the room - he's standing at the edge of the pool beside a pillar."
				},
